-- Mediaset Wins Free-To-Air Broadcasting Rights for Champions League Matches
-- B y   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i   a n d   M a r c o   B e r t a c c h e
-- 2010-12-22T11:08:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-22/mediaset-wins-free-to-air-broadcasting-rights-for-champions-league-matches.html
Mediaset SpA was awarded free-to-air
UEFA Champions League television rights to broadcast matches
including 16 exclusive Wednesday live matches and the final, the
soccer teams association said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chiara Remondini in Milan at 
